# -------- OKX broker (TESTNET / paper trading) -------------------------
# Get testnet keys at: https://www.okx.com/vi/demo-trading
# After login: Profile -> API -> Create API key
# Permissions: Read + Trade, NO Withdraw
# These get consumed by `vibe-trading connector configure okx-paper-trade`
